side...it makes it easier for
them to resupply and so North

00:02:06.831 --> 00:02:10.360
Africa is kind of defined by
this constant back and forth.

00:02:10.360 --> 00:02:14.527
But, by early 1941, it looks
like the Axis is on the

00:02:15.399 --> 00:02:18.255
offensive, able to push the
British back into Egypt lay

00:02:18.255 --> 00:02:21.413
siege to the town of Tobruk.

